team_milk <- milk %>%
  filter(state %in% c("Texas", "Colorado", "California", "Tennessee", "Illinois"))  

national <- milk %>%
  group_by(year) %>%
  summarise(milk = mean(milk_million))

team_milk$average <- national$milk
